                  <summary>Antiphonary for the Fast of Lent, ጾመ፡ ድጓ፡, with musical notation, owned by Nǝburä ‘Ǝdǝ Dǝmeṭǝros Gäbrä Maryam</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="91v" facs="005"/><title>Antiphonary for the Fast of Lent, Ṣomä Dǝggwa, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጾመ፡ ድጓ፡</foreign></title><incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ንዌጥን፡ በረድኤተ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ጽሒፈ፡ ጾመ ድጓ፡ በመሐትወ፡ ድራር፡ ጾም፡ በ፪ ሃሌ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ዘወረደ፡ እምላዕሉ፡ አይሁድ፡ ሰቀሉ፡ ወሚመ፡ ኢያእመሩ፡ እግዚአ፡ ኵሉ፡ ዘየሐዩ፡ በቃሉ፡</incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>(incorrectly labeled Book of the Sabbath of the Faith [Sänbätä Amin] on the inside cover)</note>
                  <note>Incipit (spanning the two columns)</note>
